-- 2012-01-30T22:04:49Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-30/brazil-s-hrt-advances-2-8-percent-reversing-initial-slide.html
HRT Participacoes em Petroleo SA ,
 Brazil ’s fourth-largest oil company by market value, gained,
erasing initial losses.  HRT rose 2.8 percent to 473 reais at the close of trading
in Sao Paulo, paring its decline this year to 17 percent. The
stock plunged 5.7 percent earlier in the day before rebounding.  To contact the reporter on this story:
